"tag-manners-adab","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-prayer-al-salat"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3oi","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":41153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/08\/makkah-quds-masjid-aqsa\/","url_meta":{"origin":13038,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Mecca, Jerusalem, then earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: I asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about the first mosque placed on the earth. The Prophet said, \u201cIt was the Sacred Mosque.\u201d I asked, \u201cThen which one?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe furthest mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d I said, \u201cHow long was between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/13\/ummah-honored-three-ways\/","url_meta":{"origin":13038,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Muslim nation honored for worship in three ways","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWe have been favored in three ways: Our prayer rows have been made like the rows of angels, the entire earth has been made a place of prayer for us, and its soil is purifying for ablution\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"