haram-masjid-qubur\/","url_meta":{"origin":13038,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Prohibition of building mosques in graveyards","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah reported: Anas ibn Malik, may Allah be pleased with him, passed by a graveyard of Ramad while they were building a mosque over it. Anas said, \u201cIt is hated to build a mosque in the midst of graves.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2679 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36761,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/04\/prophet-given-five\/","url_meta":{"origin":13038,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nubuwwa: The Prophet is given five unique blessings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have been given five that were given to no one before me: every prophet was sent specifically to his people but I have been sent to every white and black person, spoils are made\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13038","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/w